title: #164: Hip Hop Slop Shop (@PeteDavidson, @BrickStoneNews)
itunes:title: Hip Hop Slop Shop with Pete Davidson, Dave Sirus
description: Pete Davidson came over to my apartment in LA to talk to me about rap and hip hop. He brought his friend Dave Sirus. And lucky he did, too, because Pete was super distracted checking tweets from his first network TV set airing. It was still a fun discussion and I am now a huge Juicy J fan.
